---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
---

<MainLayout title="SMB Marketplace & Fintech Ecosystem">
  <h1>SMB Marketplace & Fintech Ecosystem</h1>

  <p style="font-size: 22px; margin-top: 16px;">
    Designing an integrated marketplace and financial services ecosystem for small
    and medium-sized businesses in Latin America.
  </p>

  <div style="margin-top: 32px; border-top: 1px solid var(--divider);"></div>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Context</h2>
    <p>
      Small and medium-sized businesses across Latin America faced fragmented tools,
      limited access to financial services, and inefficient procurement processes.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Challenge</h2>
    <p>
      How might we create a unified platform that simplifies procurement, improves
      operational visibility, and unlocks financial services for SMBs?
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Approach</h2>
    <p>
      Led a mixed-methods research approach combining interviews, surveys, and market
      analysis to deeply understand SMB workflows and constraints.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section style="margin-top: 48px;">
    <h2>Outcome</h2>
    <p>
      Delivered a platform concept that improved efficiency, increased access to
      financial tools, and created a scalable foundation for growth.
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>